com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.util

Class RandomUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.util.RandomUtil

  • public class RandomUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides static utility helper methods for generating random data sets, wells, sets, plates and stacks.
    Author:
    Jesse L. Mull
